{{PoliticsAF}} The '''Afghan Ministry of Education''' ({{lang-ps|د افغانستان د پوهنې وزارت|links=no}})is responsible for policy formulation, the organization and supervision of education in [[Afghanistan]].<ref>[http://moe.gov.af Afghanistan - Ministry of Education]</ref> Its headquarters is located in [[Kabul]]. The current Education Minister is Assadullah Hanif Balkhi. The Ministry of Education provides a [[annual report|semi-annual report]] to inform the public of advancements in Afghanistan's [[education]] sector.<ref>http://moe.gov.af/en/page/1831/3031</ref>
