'''Siddhartha Shikshya Sadan''' {{flag|Nepal}}

Siddhartha Shikshya Sadan is a Lower Secondary School in Ramdhuni Municipality ward no. 8(previously Dumraha-3, Sunsari). It was established in 2061 B.S.This school aimed in giving education with motto "learn the truth". Students from around the village are enrolled.

Nowadays, a reform is made in this school. A program "Shrasta Sanga Balbalika" is launched. This program aims in providing platform for students in out bringing their hidden talents. After successfully launch of this program over three years, it has been very effective. 

Similarly, initiation has been done to involve students in the field of Science and Technology.
[[File:Students with cyclist.jpg|alt=students of Siddhartha Shikshya Sadan|thumb|Students with cyclist Bhakta Khawas in world tour]]

